<div class="rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-primary-200 text-light" style="color:#FFFFFF;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:2:63"><h1 style="text-align:center;">Come Worship With Us</h1>

<p style="text-align:center;">
	The love of God is at the heart of what we do. Our service-oriented approach to faith is shared each Sunday at services in Winston-Salem and Kernersville. We invite you to join us for worship services at one of our two locations.
</p></div>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:3:88"></div>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:5:8"></div>
